    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart is the S65 4.0L V8, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen features a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for precise torque vectoring. Mechanically, it is superlative: the rod bearings and throttle actuators have been addressed, ensuring long-term reliability. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing a broad spectrum of suspension kinematics. The bodywork is entirely original with consistent paint depth readings across all panels, and the interior demonstrates zero bolster wear or UV degradation. A comprehensive service dossier accompanies this mechanically transparent, showroom-standard vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
